  {
    "Id": 4,
    "Content": "\n### Git",
    "ContentSha": "Jsk/nSewRFWXLXFj7CJNHoOudh5N1dZMUuaeeNEnZtQ=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n### Git",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 5,
    "Content": "```bash\n# Linux/macOS\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git ~/.config/yazi/plugins/ouch.yazi\n\n# Windows with cmd\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git %AppData%\\yazi\\config\\plugins\\ouch.yazi\n\n# Windows with powershell\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git \"$($env:APPDATA)\\yazi\\config\\plugins\\ouch.yazi\"\n```",
    "ContentSha": "TLDP5HPlY1wp1GIvn8Mid/RHSPREaO9khYZBQkxTVuo=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```bash\n# Linux/macOS\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git ~/.config/yazi/plugins/ouch.yazi\n\n# Windows with cmd\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git %AppData%\\yazi\\config\\plugins\\ouch.yazi\n\n# Windows with powershell\ngit clone https://github.com/ndtoan96/ouch.yazi.git \"$($env:APPDATA)\\yazi\\config\\plugins\\ouch.yazi\"\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 6,
    "Content": "\nMake sure you have [ouch](https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch) installed and in your `PATH`.\n\n## Usage\n\n### Preview\nFor archive preview, add this to your `yazi.toml`:\n",
    "ContentSha": "aErGIduzgzzjUfAyHhh/9Ne8vhfS5lhKSHTXTc06tO4=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\nAsegúrate de tener instalado [ouch](https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch) y que esté en tu `PATH`.\n\n## Uso\n\n### Vista previa\nPara la vista previa de archivos, añade esto a tu `yazi.toml`:\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 7,
    "Content": "```toml\n[[plugin.prepend_previewers]]\nmime = \"application/{*zip,tar,bzip2,7z*,rar,xz,zstd,java-archive}\"\nrun  = \"ouch\"\n```",
    "ContentSha": "Xp4KFjsx6gDoc0saXaPRN6h78NGvMNBDnuQ/3jH9X+E=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```toml\n[[plugin.prepend_previewers]]\nmime = \"application/{*zip,tar,bzip2,7z*,rar,xz,zstd,java-archive}\"\nrun  = \"ouch\"\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 8,
    "Content": "\nNow go to an archive on Yazi, you should see the archive's content in the preview pane. You can use `J` and `K` to roll up and down the preview.\n\n#### Customization\n\nPreviews can be customized by adding extra arguments in the `run` string:\n",
    "ContentSha": "/qHIm47DniMVp24GlsNPd5pVy8Yfp0ngCbVOAfF7jrc=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\nAhora ve a un archivo en Yazi, deberías ver el contenido del archivo en el panel de vista previa. Puedes usar `J` y `K` para desplazarte hacia arriba y abajo en la vista previa.\n\n#### Personalización\n\nLas vistas previas se pueden personalizar añadiendo argumentos adicionales en la cadena `run`:\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 9,
    "Content": "```toml\n[plugin]\nprepend_previewers = [\n\t# Change the top-level archive icon\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon='🗄️ '\" },\n\t# Or remove it by setting it to ''\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon=''\" },\n\n\t# Enable file icons\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --show-file-icons\" },\n\n\t# Disable tree view\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --list-view\" },\n\n\t# These can be combined\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon='🗄️ ' --show-file-icons --list-view\" },\n]\n```",
    "ContentSha": "zve0qhs+WwJz3LFlcmdC7THrWG2Wj75VGzFaDOeOrSk=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```toml\n[plugin]\nprepend_previewers = [\n\t# Change the top-level archive icon\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon='🗄️ '\" },\n\t# Or remove it by setting it to ''\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon=''\" },\n\n\t# Enable file icons\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --show-file-icons\" },\n\n\t# Disable tree view\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --list-view\" },\n\n\t# These can be combined\n\t{ ..., run = \"ouch --archive-icon='🗄️ ' --show-file-icons --list-view\" },\n]\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 10,
    "Content": "\n### Compression\nFor compression, add this to your `keymap.toml`:\n",
    "ContentSha": "x0YSM5SRqW/ZhAhhUCYntRZ0qFhGzrN9fqDau2T7pRw=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n### Compresión\nPara la compresión, añade esto a tu `keymap.toml`:\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 11,
    "Content": "```toml\n[[mgr.prepend_keymap]]\non = [\"C\"]\nrun = \"plugin ouch\"\ndesc = \"Compress with ouch\"\n```",
    "ContentSha": "LKCiqXToHZQokQNDC9t+TGKAc1xfzOs3W4NfKT5F3+g=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```toml\n[[mgr.prepend_keymap]]\non = [\"C\"]\nrun = \"plugin ouch\"\ndesc = \"Compress with ouch\"\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 12,
    "Content": "\nThe plugin uses `zip` format by default. You can change the format when you name the output file, `ouch` will detect format based on file extension.\n\nAnd, for example, if you would like to set `7z` as default format, you can use `plugin ouch 7z`.\n\n### Decompression\nThis plugin does not provide a decompression feature because it already is supported by Yazi.\nTo decompress with `ouch`, configure the opener in `yazi.toml`.\n",
    "ContentSha": "nHW0Bwr5WeRAAaXx2YBpRp18jKygPvqENnCouYlaa30=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\nEl plugin utiliza el formato `zip` por defecto. Puedes cambiar el formato al nombrar el archivo de salida, `ouch` detectará el formato según la extensión del archivo.\n\nY, por ejemplo, si deseas establecer `7z` como formato predeterminado, puedes usar `plugin ouch 7z`.\n\n### Descompresión\nEste plugin no proporciona una función de descompresión porque ya está soportada por Yazi.\nPara descomprimir con `ouch`, configura el abridor en `yazi.toml`.\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 13,
    "Content": "```toml\n[opener]\nextract = [\n\t{ run = 'ouch d -y %*', desc = \"Extract here with ouch\", for = \"windows\" },\n\t{ run = 'ouch d -y \"$@\"', desc = \"Extract here with ouch\", for = \"unix\" },\n]\n```",
    "ContentSha": "IxnzOBZlInfB+8UPzGSS0ozQr+H8V7e50MKHSb3cLO0=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```toml\n[opener]\nextract = [\n\t{ run = 'ouch d -y %*', desc = \"Extract here with ouch\", for = \"windows\" },\n\t{ run = 'ouch d -y \"$@\"', desc = \"Extract here with ouch\", for = \"unix\" },\n]\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
